tonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Feb 05, 2026</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104yfd1665703273621.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/yfd1665703273621.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/yfd1665703273621.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"yfd1665703273621\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      /lse\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Copy language setups to an XML file.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"yfd1665703273621__section_w2497ab1b5b1_w2498ab1b5_w2499ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"yfd1665703273621__p_d150173e1_d150174e1_d150175e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/lse</span> {<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/lan=</span>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Language</var>} {<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/var=</span>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Library</var>} <var class=\"keyword varname\">FileName</var>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"yfd1665703273621__section_w2500ab1b5b3_w2501ab1b5_w2502ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1186332e76\">\n                  \n Switches\n </h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"yfd1665703273621__li_d52217e1_d52218e1_d52219e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"yet1665703273551.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yet1665703273551.html\" title=\"Specify the language to be exported.\">/lan=</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"yfd1665703273621__li_d52220e1_d52221e1_d52222e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jet1719657364758.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jet1719657364758.html\" title=\"Specify library for export.\">/var=</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"yfd1665703273621__section_w2503ab1b5b5_w2504ab1b5_w2505ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1186332e105\">\n                  \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"yfd1665703273621__p_d150182e1_d150183e1_d150184e1\">Copy the source for the language setup identified by <var class=\"keyword varname\">Language</var> and <var class=\"keyword varname\">Library</var> to <var class=\"keyword varname\">File</var>. The export format is XML.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"yfd1665703273621__p_d150185e1_d150186e1_d150187e1\">If the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/lan</span> sub-switch is omitted, all the languages in library are copied.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"yfd1665703273621__p_d150188e1_d150189e1_d150190e1\">If the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/var</span> sub-switch is omitted, the versions of language from all libraries are copied to file.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"yfd1665703273621__p_d150191e1_d150192e1_d150193e1\">If both the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/lan</span> and the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/var</span> sub-switches are omitted, all language setups are copied.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"yfd1665703273621__p_d150194e1_d150195e1_d150196e1\">Remember that when you copy these definitions from <var class=\"keyword varname\">File</var> into a Repository, you must compile the language setups before they can be used. Use the command line switch <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/mes</span> or choose <span class=\"ph menucascade\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">File &gt;Compile</span></span> from one of the language setup editors.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"yfd1665703273621__section_w2506ab1b5b7_w2507ab1b5_w2508ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1186332e160\">Example: Using /lse </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"yfd1665703273621__p_d150200e1_d150201e1_d150202e1\">The following example copies all language setups from the library MYLIB to the file <span class=\"ph filepath\">lang.xml</span>:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">/lse /var=MYLIB /lan=USA lang.xml?</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ddc1665702657086.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>/mes</a><p>Compile global messages, help texts, and language setups.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2534064\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2534064\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "/lse Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Feb 05, 2026 Summarize Uniface 10.4 /lse Copy language setups to an XML file. /lse { /lan= Language } { /var= Library } FileName Switches /lan= /var= Description Copy the source for the language setup identified by Language and Library to File . The export format is XML. If the /lan sub-switch is omitted, all the languages in library are copied. If the /var sub-switch is omitted, the versions of language from all libraries are copied to file. If both the /lan and the /var sub-switches are omitted, all language setups are copied. Remember that when you copy these definitions from File into a Repository, you must compile the language setups before they can be used. Use the command line switch /mes or choose File >Compile from one of the language setup editors. Example: Using /lse The following example copies all language setups from the library MYLIB to the file lang.xml : /lse /var=MYLIB /lan=USA lang.xml? Copy Related Links /mes Compile global messages, help texts, and language setups. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}